# Coding Patterns: {{projectName}}

> Generated by @nakedev/nest-scaffold

## Structure

- `src/common/` — cross-cutting concerns
- `src/modules/<feature>/` — feature modules
- `dto/` — request validation
- `entities/` — TypeORM entities
- `queries/` — filter chain query builders
- `swagger/` — API documentation decorators

## Conventions

- Controllers: routing and validation only
- Services: business logic
- Query classes: data access with filter chains
- Throw `AppException.from(ERROR)` for domain errors
